'''Order GAO-1133B''' was a law passed by the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] stating that major defense firms could only produce weaponry for the [[Galactic Alliance Defense Force]], with limited amounts suitable only for their own planetary defense being the sole exception.

